Package it.unibs.fp.codiceFiscale

Class FiscalCode

java.lang.Object
it.unibs.fp.codiceFiscale.FiscalCode
public class FiscalCode extends Object
Manages the different part of a fiscal code FST-PLA-98-M-01-B157-E: surname(3), name(3), yearBirth(2), monthBirth(1), dayBirth(2), birthPlace(1, 2), controlCharacter(1)
